casebody.data:
First Department,

July, 1975

(July 1, 1975) ASR Iron Works, Inc., et al., Respondents, v Suburbia Construction Corp. et al., Appellants, et al., Defendants.

Order, Supreme Court, New York County, entered on December 23, 1974, unanimously affirmed, without costs and without disbursements, the respondents having neither appeared nor filed a brief. No opinion. Concur—Stevens, P. J., Murphy, Lupiano, Lane and Nunez, JJ.
